d thought of comparing his State grammar school with an Independent or a Direct Grant school at a later stage of his research, and}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6708948  he didn\rquote 
