, so I thought, \'93Right!\'94  They were both working in Salford, so I got on a bike and began cycling around Salford till I found the worst looking schoo
l I could find, which was a worn out sec. mod. opposite the docks in Salford, and I went back and said, \'93I think I should go there\'94.  So the Department then arranged a meeting with the Director of Education, and in those days they were rather gra}{
