d made one slight error.  And then I was suddenly told I\rquote d have to teach the maths!  Would I teach the maths?  Well, I couldn\rquote t say no, they\rquote d taken me on in the school, so I began teaching this guy\rquote 
s timetable.  Well, it became a famous story later, because I went in, and they were up to, I don\rquote 
t know what it was - volume of a cylinder, or volume of a cone or something, so I looked up the relevant pi formula, and we went through a couple of these, and then I set them the work, and set the homework and I
